55.1	The_Day_the_Earth_Stood_Still_(2008_film)	The Day the Earth Stood Still (2008 film)	The Day the Earth Stood Still is a 2008 science fiction film, a remake of the 1951 film of the same name. The screenplay is based on the 1940 classic science fiction short story "Farewell to the Master" by Harry Bates, and the 1951 screenplay adaptation by Edmund H. North.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c1/The_Day_the_Earth_Stood_Still.jpg/220px-The_Day_the_Earth_Stood_Still.jpg
